# Part 7 - Active Directory Structure, Shared Folders, Permissions, and Mapped Drives

## Overview
In this section, we build a proper enterprise-style Active Directory structure using Organizational Units (OUs), Security Groups, and Users. We then create dedicated shared folders for each department, apply permissions using Security Groups, and map network drives from the Windows 11 workstation.

---

## Environment
| Machine | Role | IP Address |
|---|---|---|
| Windows Server 2022 VM (Ceres-DC-01) | Domain Controller / File Server | 10.0.0.10 |
| Windows 11 VM | Domain-joined Workstation | 10.0.0.x |
| Domain | example.com | — |

